WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:02:19.831 --> 00:02:22.527
Cheers!

3
00:02:30.442 --> 00:02:31.841
Excellent.

4
00:02:32.410 --> 00:02:34.640
Let's drink until we drop.

5
00:02:34.946 --> 00:02:36.573
Save something for your wife.

6
00:02:36.815 --> 00:02:39.545
Are you kidding?

7
00:02:39.918 --> 00:02:42.250
Alcohol revives me.

8
00:02:42.454 --> 00:02:45.014
The later it gets. the hornier I get.

9
00:02:45.356 --> 00:02:48.985
Another glass. A little sip.

10
00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:53.993
Tell me. Jane...

11
00:02:54.532 --> 00:02:55.829
What year are you in?

12
00:02:56.201 --> 00:02:56.860
4th year.

13
00:02:57.068 --> 00:02:59.263
A senior should know better.

14
00:02:59.504 --> 00:03:01.938
What are you doing with Tun?

15
00:03:02.373 --> 00:03:03.601
He's a hunk.

16
00:03:03.842 --> 00:03:06.310
You keep saying that.

17
00:03:06.544 --> 00:03:09.172
Making Jim ask for girl's numbers.

18
00:03:09.414 --> 00:03:10.142
Then breaking their hearts.

19
00:03:10.381 --> 00:03:13.714
Speaking of broken hearts...

20
00:03:13.918 --> 00:03:15.317
Remember the time...

21
00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:18.751
that girl left him a drunken mess.

22
00:03:19.090 --> 00:03:20.057
Her name was Kay.

23
00:03:20.291 --> 00:03:21.952
Ignore them.

24
00:03:23.928 --> 00:03:26.021
Wait. I have a question.

25
00:03:26.331 --> 00:03:28.196
How can a guy like you get married?

26
00:03:28.399 --> 00:03:29.832
What's wrong with me?

27
00:03:30.535 --> 00:03:33.095
After a long tiring day...

28
00:03:33.471 --> 00:03:35.029
I want to head home...

29
00:03:35.373 --> 00:03:37.671
to a wife's embrace or a pet's face.

30
00:03:37.876 --> 00:03:39.343
Not waste my life...

31
00:03:39.911 --> 00:03:41.970
partying with you losers.

32
00:03:42.213 --> 00:03:43.840
Not with me.

33
00:03:44.749 --> 00:03:45.841
A good man...

34
00:03:46.284 --> 00:03:48.616
who went whoring with me last night.

35
00:03:50.188 --> 00:03:51.849
Fooling around so soon?

36
00:03:53.258 --> 00:03:54.520
Here she comes.

37
00:03:57.061 --> 00:03:57.720
Quiet.

38
00:03:57.929 --> 00:03:58.987
What's so funny?

39
00:04:00.732 --> 00:04:01.721
Nothing.

40
00:04:02.166 --> 00:04:04.430
One last thing...

41
00:04:05.169 --> 00:04:07.069
One more glass!

42
00:04:26.124 --> 00:04:27.421
What are we listening to?

43
00:04:29.727 --> 00:04:30.921
Don't turn it off.

44
00:04:31.129 --> 00:04:32.460
It's beautiful.

45
00:04:35.133 --> 00:04:36.828
You guys seem tight.

46
00:04:37.068 --> 00:04:38.660
Do you meet often?

47
00:04:42.440 --> 00:04:43.566
What are you looking at?

48
00:04:44.375 --> 00:04:45.740
Beautiful you.

49
00:04:48.112 --> 00:04:49.340
What a sap.

50
00:05:31.456 --> 00:05:32.923
Are you hurt?

51
00:05:34.659 --> 00:05:35.921
Tun...

52
00:05:36.861 --> 00:05:38.385
Is she dead?

53
00:05:46.738 --> 00:05:48.103
Wait!

54
00:05:57.649 --> 00:05:58.843
Drive away.

55
00:05:59.517 --> 00:06:01.144
I said drive away!

56
00:06:02.353 --> 00:06:03.752
Drive away!

57
00:06:13.931 --> 00:06:15.728
Get closer. please.

58
00:06:16.334 --> 00:06:17.301
Okay.

59
00:06:18.336 --> 00:06:19.769
Big smile. Nuch.

60
00:06:20.571 --> 00:06:21.868
Or you won't look pretty.

61
00:06:30.181 --> 00:06:31.705
All Science Majors...

62
00:06:31.949 --> 00:06:34.144
gather for a class photo.

63
00:06:34.652 --> 00:06:35.880
They're calling you.

64
00:06:36.921 --> 00:06:38.047
Where's Jane?

65
00:06:39.490 --> 00:06:41.924
Taking photos with her friends.

66
00:06:43.061 --> 00:06:45.222
I though maybe you broke up.

67
00:06:46.130 --> 00:06:47.722
Come! Let's go.

68
00:07:42.887 --> 00:07:44.980
I phoned but you didn't pick up.

69
00:07:45.356 --> 00:07:46.516
Was it on silent?

70
00:07:55.533 --> 00:07:57.160
Nuch asked about you today.

71
00:08:00.538 --> 00:08:02.301
When will you be free?

72
00:08:02.540 --> 00:08:04.440
She wants to...

73
00:08:25.830 --> 00:08:27.024
Jane.

74
00:08:28.766 --> 00:08:30.427
How can you act like this?

75
00:08:34.272 --> 00:08:36.263
Pretending nothing happened.

76
00:08:38.442 --> 00:08:39.568
Since that night...

77
00:08:39.811 --> 00:08:41.403
I haven't slept soundly.

78
00:08:45.349 --> 00:08:47.044
I'm upset as well.

79
00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:51.452
At least we should have checked.

80
00:08:53.357 --> 00:08:55.518
It was an accident.

81
00:08:56.794 --> 00:08:58.455
That's easy for you to say.

82
00:08:59.964 --> 00:09:01.693
You weren't behind the wheel.

83
00:09:13.811 --> 00:09:15.335
- Hi. Ti.
- Hey.

84
00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:17.643
How's business?

85
00:09:17.949 --> 00:09:19.917
With you here this early...

86
00:09:20.318 --> 00:09:22.218
business should be bad.

87
00:09:23.955 --> 00:09:25.752
Are my prints ready?

88
00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:28.420
Yeah. Just a sec.

89
00:09:33.331 --> 00:09:34.389
Here.

90
00:09:57.688 --> 00:09:58.985
Is your processor broken?

91
00:10:00.491 --> 00:10:01.617
Let's see.

92
00:10:06.430 --> 00:10:07.692
The nerve.

93
00:10:07.899 --> 00:10:09.264
Nice prints and you're great.

94
00:10:09.467 --> 00:10:11.901
If they suck. it's my fault.

95
00:10:12.270 --> 00:10:13.669
Let's check the negative.

96
00:10:14.639 --> 00:10:15.867
No way.

97
00:10:16.073 --> 00:10:17.404
I took them. I should know.

98
00:10:17.642 --> 00:10:18.734
We'll see.

99
00:10:21.112 --> 00:10:22.204
See.

100
00:10:23.514 --> 00:10:25.175
Your negative are bad.

101
00:10:48.339 --> 00:10:49.499
Tun.

102
00:10:59.750 --> 00:11:01.149
Tun.

103
00:11:17.835 --> 00:11:19.132
Tun.

104
00:11:21.138 --> 00:11:22.571
Can you hear me?

105
00:13:26.363 --> 00:13:27.660
Help!

106
00:13:28.732 --> 00:13:30.290
Help!

107
00:14:02.933 --> 00:14:05.401
Don't be scared. I'm here now.

108
00:14:25.122 --> 00:14:26.487
What's wrong with your camera?

109
00:14:27.825 --> 00:14:28.792
I don't' know.

110
00:14:28.993 --> 00:14:30.517
The whole roll is ruined.

111
00:14:33.164 --> 00:14:34.859
That many?

112
00:14:40.571 --> 00:14:42.129
What are these shadows?

113
00:14:43.174 --> 00:14:44.835
My camera must be broken.

114
00:14:46.911 --> 00:14:48.640
How should I tell Nuch?

115
00:14:52.583 --> 00:14:53.880
Tun...

116
00:14:55.352 --> 00:14:56.751
Look at this picture.

117
00:15:07.898 --> 00:15:09.058
That woman...

118
00:15:10.201 --> 00:15:11.532
Do you think she's dead?

119
00:15:12.269 --> 00:15:13.327
That's enough.

120
00:15:18.642 --> 00:15:20.940
I'll have my camera fixed tomorrow.

121
00:16:23.340 --> 00:16:24.170
Tun...

122
00:16:24.375 --> 00:16:25.706
Look at this picture.

123
00:16:49.533 --> 00:16:51.091
Are you sure it was here?

124
00:16:58.342 --> 00:16:59.240
Excuse me.

125
00:16:59.443 --> 00:17:00.410
What happened?

126
00:17:00.844 --> 00:17:04.245
A few days ago a car hit the billboard.

127
00:17:04.682 --> 00:17:05.910
Must have been drunk.

128
00:17:07.918 --> 00:17:09.886
Was anyone hurt?

129
00:17:10.921 --> 00:17:12.013
No.

130
00:17:12.556 --> 00:17:13.887
Just the broken sign.

131
00:17:14.124 --> 00:17:15.421
Are you sure?

132
00:17:15.659 --> 00:17:16.523
What?

133
00:17:17.995 --> 00:17:19.553
Nothing.

134
00:17:20.864 --> 00:17:22.058
Thank you.

135
00:17:24.034 --> 00:17:25.126
What?

136
00:17:27.304 --> 00:17:29.431
You sure you checked everywhere?

137
00:17:32.943 --> 00:17:34.240
Nothing.

138
00:17:34.912 --> 00:17:36.140
Thanks anyways.

139
00:17:41.018 --> 00:17:43.418
He called every precinct and hospital.

140
00:17:45.022 --> 00:17:48.458
No accidents were reported that night.

141
00:17:48.859 --> 00:17:50.258
That's not possible.

142
00:17:51.462 --> 00:17:53.191
What about the girl we hit?

143
00:17:54.865 --> 00:17:57.095
You sure he called every one?

144
00:17:57.368 --> 00:17:59.131
Maybe someone helped her.

145
00:17:59.703 --> 00:18:01.568
Maybe she's fine.

146
00:18:01.839 --> 00:18:03.204
How could she be fine?

147
00:18:03.440 --> 00:18:05.203
We ploughed her down.

148
00:18:08.212 --> 00:18:09.873
And even if she's fine...

149
00:18:11.482 --> 00:18:13.143
Something is in those pictures.

150
00:18:13.617 --> 00:18:16.245
I told you they're not related to her.

151
00:18:16.754 --> 00:18:17.880
They're just bad exposures.

152
00:18:18.088 --> 00:18:19.521
Get it?

153
00:19:20.951 --> 00:19:21.975
Tun...

154
00:19:22.653 --> 00:19:24.245
You need to make some merit.

155
00:19:25.722 --> 00:19:26.882
These pictures...

156
00:19:27.257 --> 00:19:29.452
show that a spirit is haunting you.

157
00:19:35.732 --> 00:19:38.132
How long have you been a photographer?

158
00:19:38.335 --> 00:19:39.962
Why are you showing me these?

159
00:19:40.304 --> 00:19:41.202
I know...

160
00:19:41.705 --> 00:19:43.832
But don't you find these shadows strange?

161
00:19:46.343 --> 00:19:47.640
You want to see spirits?

162
00:19:48.645 --> 00:19:49.873
I'll show you some.

163
00:19:57.855 --> 00:19:58.583
Here.

164
00:19:59.289 --> 00:20:00.415
Auntie Cham's spirit.

165
00:20:01.425 --> 00:20:02.722
You know where she is now?

166
00:20:05.729 --> 00:20:08.493
She's selling grilled bananas next door.

167
00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:11.531
Here's Auntie Cham. And here.

168
00:20:12.269 --> 00:20:13.327
All Auntie Cham.

169
00:20:13.871 --> 00:20:15.065
Taken on the same day.

170
00:20:15.439 --> 00:20:16.599
They're just double exposures...

171
00:20:16.840 --> 00:20:18.307
and out of focus.

172
00:20:19.243 --> 00:20:22.041
Come on. I know that.

173
00:20:30.354 --> 00:20:32.447
Everyone is familiar with this place.

174
00:20:33.991 --> 00:20:36.255
Just an ordinary location...

175
00:20:37.628 --> 00:20:39.220
that we pass...

176
00:20:39.830 --> 00:20:41.320
and see everyday.

177
00:20:46.870 --> 00:20:48.735
Now look at these pictures...

178
00:20:52.643 --> 00:20:55.441
taken of the same place.

179
00:20:56.280 --> 00:20:57.542
In these...

180
00:20:58.682 --> 00:21:00.240
the bridge looks nicer.

181
00:21:02.452 --> 00:21:03.714
That means photography...

182
00:21:04.154 --> 00:21:08.420
does not reproduce reality.

183
00:21:10.761 --> 00:21:12.058
It depends on how...

184
00:21:13.063 --> 00:21:15.657
the image is framed.

185
00:21:16.266 --> 00:21:17.756
What is revealed.

186
00:21:18.135 --> 00:21:19.762
What is concealed.

187
00:21:20.971 --> 00:21:23.565
Your perspective is critical.

188
00:21:34.918 --> 00:21:38.445
"Special Scoop: Spirit Pictures"

189
00:21:50.934 --> 00:21:52.333
Jane. you're early.

190
00:21:54.805 --> 00:21:56.033
I'll get it.

191
00:22:01.044 --> 00:22:02.705
- Hello?
- Hello. Tun.

192
00:22:02.946 --> 00:22:04.914
It's Jane. I'll come by later.

193
00:22:06.350 --> 00:22:07.044
Hello?

194
00:22:07.284 --> 00:22:09.343
Tun. can you hear me?

195
00:22:09.586 --> 00:22:10.814
Hello?

196
00:22:11.021 --> 00:22:12.283
Tun!

197
00:22:12.522 --> 00:22:13.784
Tun!

198
00:22:14.524 --> 00:22:15.582
Hello?

199
00:22:15.792 --> 00:22:17.316
Hello?

200
00:22:44.688 --> 00:22:45.950
What's wrong?

201
00:22:46.757 --> 00:22:47.724
I don't' know.

202
00:22:47.924 --> 00:22:49.892
My neck's hurt since the accident.

203
00:22:50.961 --> 00:22:52.622
You should go see a doctor.

204
00:22:54.531 --> 00:22:55.793
I'm sure it's not serious.

205
00:22:59.236 --> 00:23:00.863
What's the use of talking to these spoofs?

206
00:23:02.539 --> 00:23:05.030
"Real Ghosts"

207
00:23:07.544 --> 00:23:08.943
Are you a reporter?

208
00:23:09.212 --> 00:23:10.236
No.

209
00:23:11.314 --> 00:23:13.782
The funeral foundation sent us.

210
00:23:16.019 --> 00:23:18.214
We run a legal operation.

211
00:23:18.522 --> 00:23:20.285
We have all the right permits.

212
00:24:07.771 --> 00:24:08.829
Excuse me.

213
00:24:09.272 --> 00:24:11.570
Are all these pictures fakes?

214
00:24:13.210 --> 00:24:15.542
Piak! Tell the boss he has guests.

215
00:24:18.381 --> 00:24:19.712
Everyone fakes them.

216
00:24:21.218 --> 00:24:22.242
You know...

217
00:24:22.519 --> 00:24:24.384
these photos are always a hit.

218
00:24:25.555 --> 00:24:27.546
Any issue with them sells out.

219
00:24:28.625 --> 00:24:29.592
But you think...

220
00:24:30.026 --> 00:24:31.721
we can always find real ones?

221
00:24:33.997 --> 00:24:36.158
Isn't that deceiving the public?

222
00:24:37.567 --> 00:24:39.262
Our readers...

223
00:24:39.903 --> 00:24:41.894
want to see scary photos.

224
00:24:43.240 --> 00:24:44.798
They don't want loves stories.

225
00:24:46.543 --> 00:24:49.944
Does that mean every photo is fake?

226
00:24:53.049 --> 00:24:54.880
I didn't say that.

227
00:25:08.431 --> 00:25:09.557
Take a look.

228
00:25:10.534 --> 00:25:11.933
See anything?

229
00:25:12.569 --> 00:25:14.867
This is the first photo I had.

230
00:25:16.106 --> 00:25:17.471
I took it at home.

231
00:25:19.242 --> 00:25:20.470
The shadow...

232
00:25:20.744 --> 00:25:23.212
bears a likeness to my mom.

233
00:25:26.550 --> 00:25:28.245
Believe what you will.

234
00:25:30.353 --> 00:25:31.445
But this picture...

235
00:25:32.255 --> 00:25:35.088
was taken after she passed away.

236
00:25:37.093 --> 00:25:38.492
You know...

237
00:25:38.762 --> 00:25:39.751
sometimes...

238
00:25:39.963 --> 00:25:42.397
spirits long for their loved ones.

239
00:25:48.638 --> 00:25:50.003
In my opinion...

240
00:25:50.874 --> 00:25:52.171
these pictures...

241
00:25:53.343 --> 00:25:54.810
represent more than...

242
00:25:55.445 --> 00:25:57.413
macabre urban legends.

243
00:25:59.649 --> 00:26:01.844
They are signs.

244
00:26:06.456 --> 00:26:07.753
Think about it.

245
00:26:09.059 --> 00:26:10.549
Why would the dead...

246
00:26:11.328 --> 00:26:12.920
return to the living...

247
00:26:16.299 --> 00:26:19.166
Without a message to convey?

248
00:26:23.473 --> 00:26:24.838
Most importantly...

249
00:26:25.742 --> 00:26:27.141
I believe...

250
00:26:28.211 --> 00:26:29.644
these shadows...

251
00:26:30.380 --> 00:26:32.848
are related to someone in the picture.

252
00:26:37.120 --> 00:26:38.382
A father...

253
00:26:38.755 --> 00:26:39.813
mother...

254
00:26:40.123 --> 00:26:41.454
or lover.

255
00:26:43.560 --> 00:26:44.822
Or someone...

256
00:26:45.028 --> 00:26:47.019
you maligned in life.

257
00:27:09.986 --> 00:27:12.648
How can we tell if they're real...

258
00:27:12.856 --> 00:27:14.187
and not fakes?

259
00:27:14.557 --> 00:27:15.990
What about Polaroid's?

260
00:27:16.192 --> 00:27:17.591
Can you fake them?

261
00:27:21.031 --> 00:27:25.400
You load the film and press the shutter.

262
00:27:25.835 --> 00:27:27.132
The photo ejects.

263
00:27:44.955 --> 00:27:46.616
Tell me then...

264
00:27:47.390 --> 00:27:49.324
How can they be faked?

265
00:27:53.263 --> 00:27:55.857
How do we know what they want?

266
00:27:56.466 --> 00:27:57.455
Perhaps...

267
00:27:57.734 --> 00:27:59.565
the answer is in the photo.

268
00:28:10.046 --> 00:28:11.911
Two more poses.

269
00:28:12.782 --> 00:28:14.215
Big smiles.

270
00:28:18.054 --> 00:28:20.614
Let's have a different pose.

271
00:28:21.257 --> 00:28:24.158
Embrace her. hold the bouquet...

272
00:28:24.361 --> 00:28:26.386
and kiss her cheek.

273
00:28:28.765 --> 00:28:29.823
Beautiful.

274
00:28:31.401 --> 00:28:33.266
We're done.

275
00:28:33.636 --> 00:28:36.002
Thank you both.

276
00:28:36.439 --> 00:28:38.634
Take them to the dressing room.

277
00:29:03.967 --> 00:29:05.298
What the...

278
00:29:07.103 --> 00:29:08.365
Who's doing that?

279
00:29:08.938 --> 00:29:10.371
Aum. check the fuse!

280
00:29:12.275 --> 00:29:13.674
Hey! Aum!

281
00:29:16.813 --> 00:29:17.643
Aum!

282
00:29:18.915 --> 00:29:20.041
Who's doing that?

283
00:29:21.317 --> 00:29:23.285
Is it you. Aum?

284
00:29:29.559 --> 00:29:30.719
Who is it?

285
00:29:33.396 --> 00:29:34.886
Aum. where are you?

286
00:29:36.933 --> 00:29:38.400
Who's there!

287
00:29:39.069 --> 00:29:40.331
I asked who it is!

288
00:29:48.411 --> 00:29:50.003
Where are you. Aum?

289
00:29:55.251 --> 00:29:56.650
Who's there!

290
00:30:45.902 --> 00:30:47.494
Please step off the scale.

291
00:30:51.074 --> 00:30:52.666
Step on it again.

292
00:31:00.483 --> 00:31:02.110
Been working hard lately?

293
00:31:02.352 --> 00:31:03.842
Not really.

294
00:31:04.487 --> 00:31:05.920
How long has it hurt?

295
00:31:06.890 --> 00:31:08.721
For quite awhile.

296
00:31:08.925 --> 00:31:10.790
But it's gotten worse lately.

297
00:31:11.261 --> 00:31:13.422
I had a car accident.

298
00:31:14.030 --> 00:31:15.292
An accident?

299
00:31:15.932 --> 00:31:17.797
