300
00:31:18.968 --> 00:31:20.299
You shouldn't worry.

301
00:31:21.237 --> 00:31:23.728
But it really hurts.

302
00:31:24.941 --> 00:31:27.102
Your x-rays are normal.

303
00:31:27.443 --> 00:31:28.967
It may be a sprain.

304
00:31:29.312 --> 00:31:31.371
Try the medicine I prescribed.

305
00:31:32.682 --> 00:31:34.741
Mr. Tun. please pick up your prescription.

306
00:31:38.721 --> 00:31:39.949
Take this medicine...

307
00:31:40.323 --> 00:31:42.587
3 times a day after meals...

308
00:31:42.859 --> 00:31:45.089
until the prescription runs out.

309
00:31:47.130 --> 00:31:48.324
Lying bastard.

310
00:31:49.532 --> 00:31:50.328
Pardon?

311
00:31:50.533 --> 00:31:51.591
Yes?

312
00:31:52.936 --> 00:31:54.426
Nothing.

313
00:31:59.075 --> 00:32:00.736
Lying bastard.

314
00:32:02.445 --> 00:32:03.742
Lying bastard.

315
00:32:04.881 --> 00:32:06.348
As for this medicine...

316
00:32:08.284 --> 00:32:08.943
Sir!

317
00:32:09.185 --> 00:32:11.050
What's wrong?

318
00:32:14.057 --> 00:32:15.615
...is rarely seen.

319
00:32:16.125 --> 00:32:18.559
When grasshoppers begin mating...

320
00:32:19.062 --> 00:32:21.997
the male smells the female...

321
00:32:22.799 --> 00:32:26.394
from a distance up to 100 meters.

322
00:32:27.203 --> 00:32:30.798
The male carefully approaches the female.

323
00:32:31.574 --> 00:32:34.634
It hooks itself onto her belly.

324
00:32:35.345 --> 00:32:37.142
And they begin to mate.

325
00:32:38.748 --> 00:32:42.445
The female's response is surprising.

326
00:32:43.620 --> 00:32:46.987
The male becomes her prey.

327
00:32:47.624 --> 00:32:51.253
She slowly eats off his head...

328
00:32:51.828 --> 00:32:54.388
while they are mating.

329
00:32:56.299 --> 00:32:57.288
Eventually...

330
00:32:57.500 --> 00:32:59.661
the male succumbs to death.

331
00:33:08.344 --> 00:33:11.643
Excuse me. where is Room 301?

332
00:33:17.987 --> 00:33:18.885
Jane.

333
00:33:22.925 --> 00:33:24.358
Jane.

334
00:33:33.803 --> 00:33:35.065
Jane.

335
00:34:43.940 --> 00:34:45.100
Who's there?

336
00:35:13.770 --> 00:35:14.896
Tonn...

337
00:35:15.805 --> 00:35:17.170
What's wrong?

338
00:35:20.743 --> 00:35:21.710
Tun...

339
00:35:21.911 --> 00:35:23.344
I'm going to die.

340
00:35:23.546 --> 00:35:25.173
What's going on?

341
00:35:25.848 --> 00:35:26.940
The photos...

342
00:35:28.551 --> 00:35:29.984
Bring me those photos.

343
00:35:31.053 --> 00:35:32.247
What photos?

344
00:35:32.522 --> 00:35:33.546
Are you drunk?

345
00:35:35.224 --> 00:35:36.555
Those photos...

346
00:35:36.993 --> 00:35:38.517
Where did you hide them?

347
00:35:38.761 --> 00:35:40.058
Give them to me.

348
00:35:41.764 --> 00:35:43.197
Remember that bitch.

349
00:35:43.466 --> 00:35:44.455
Calm down.

350
00:35:45.601 --> 00:35:46.431
What photos?

351
00:35:46.636 --> 00:35:48.263
Just give them to me!

352
00:35:48.638 --> 00:35:50.333
Please calm down.

353
00:35:51.541 --> 00:35:52.940
Tonn. calm down.

354
00:35:53.743 --> 00:35:55.142
What photos?

355
00:36:00.283 --> 00:36:01.443
Tonn.

356
00:36:01.651 --> 00:36:03.084
I'll call your wife.

357
00:36:45.928 --> 00:36:47.156
What are you doing?

358
00:36:48.698 --> 00:36:50.222
Cleaning up.

359
00:36:56.305 --> 00:36:57.738
Your neck still sore?

360
00:36:59.742 --> 00:37:00.902
Yeah.

361
00:37:01.143 --> 00:37:03.202
Take it easy. Don't work so much.

362
00:41:33.349 --> 00:41:35.146
"Natrenapa Chan-ngam. Honor Society 1995"

363
00:41:47.530 --> 00:41:48.690
Tonn.

364
00:41:49.532 --> 00:41:51.022
It's Tun.

365
00:41:52.635 --> 00:41:54.102
Are you home?

366
00:42:08.250 --> 00:42:09.342
Tonn.

367
00:42:11.654 --> 00:42:13.144
Are you home?

368
00:42:21.964 --> 00:42:23.124
Tonn.

369
00:42:47.823 --> 00:42:49.051
"Natrenapa Chan-ngam"

370
00:43:36.171 --> 00:43:37.661
Tonn!

371
00:43:38.374 --> 00:43:39.466
Tonn!

372
00:43:41.343 --> 00:43:42.503
Tonn!

373
00:43:49.451 --> 00:43:50.941
Tonn!

374
00:44:26.455 --> 00:44:29.219
I'm really sorry.

375
00:44:30.526 --> 00:44:31.754
Do you know...

376
00:44:31.994 --> 00:44:33.461
What was bothering him?

377
00:44:37.333 --> 00:44:38.857
No. Suddenly he...

378
00:44:39.068 --> 00:44:41.298
It's your gang's fault.

379
00:44:43.639 --> 00:44:45.368
Have you all gone insane?

380
00:44:46.675 --> 00:44:48.267
What do you mean?

381
00:44:49.445 --> 00:44:51.413
You've all committed suicide.

382
00:44:52.748 --> 00:44:53.874
Who?

383
00:44:55.284 --> 00:44:56.717
Don't you know?

384
00:44:57.386 --> 00:44:58.853
The other two...

385
00:44:59.254 --> 00:45:01.279
also killed themselves.

386
00:45:01.991 --> 00:45:03.219
Which two?

387
00:45:06.495 --> 00:45:10.295
The two who sat next to you.

388
00:45:54.610 --> 00:45:56.043
Who's this woman?

389
00:46:00.416 --> 00:46:01.815
Where did you get that?

390
00:46:03.085 --> 00:46:05.144
She's the shadow in the photos. right?

391
00:46:06.789 --> 00:46:07.949
Who is she?

392
00:46:10.859 --> 00:46:12.827
How is she related to you?

393
00:46:31.180 --> 00:46:33.148
I knew her in college.

394
00:46:36.251 --> 00:46:37.741
Her name is Natre.

395
00:46:41.323 --> 00:46:43.314
She was a quiet person...

396
00:46:45.060 --> 00:46:46.425
without any friends.

397
00:46:50.566 --> 00:46:52.431
We all thought she was weird.

398
00:46:57.606 --> 00:46:59.198
I felt sorry for her.

399
00:47:06.448 --> 00:47:08.643
We dated but I kept it secret.

400
00:47:12.187 --> 00:47:13.552
She loved me a lot.

401
00:50:04.726 --> 00:50:06.421
She threatened to slit her wrists.

402
00:50:08.230 --> 00:50:09.857
I didn't know what to do.

403
00:50:10.432 --> 00:50:12.127
My friends thought it was funny.

404
00:50:12.634 --> 00:50:14.158
How were they involved?

405
00:50:14.703 --> 00:50:16.000
Why are they dead?

406
00:50:16.605 --> 00:50:17.731
They...

407
00:50:17.939 --> 00:50:18.997
What did they do?

408
00:50:21.443 --> 00:50:22.671
I don't know.

409
00:50:24.046 --> 00:50:26.412
Tonn said he'd take care of it.

410
00:50:30.352 --> 00:50:32.047
After that. Natre disappeared.

411
00:50:33.889 --> 00:50:35.914
I never saw her again.

412
00:50:36.925 --> 00:50:39.018
Didn't you try to stop them?

413
00:50:41.129 --> 00:50:43.791
How could you let it happen?

414
00:50:50.339 --> 00:50:51.829
What could I do?

415
00:50:54.242 --> 00:50:55.869
Now everyone is dead.

416
00:50:59.414 --> 00:51:00.642
I'm...

417
00:51:01.616 --> 00:51:03.140
I'm going to die next.

418
00:51:41.890 --> 00:51:43.187
It's funny how...

419
00:51:45.527 --> 00:51:47.427
we always say...

420
00:51:48.363 --> 00:51:50.126
if we could turn back time...

421
00:51:51.900 --> 00:51:52.832
we...

422
00:51:53.068 --> 00:51:55.036
we would reverse all our wrongs.

423
00:51:58.440 --> 00:52:00.067
Do you think she's okay?

424
00:52:01.510 --> 00:52:02.875
Will she be there?

425
00:52:03.311 --> 00:52:04.403
Go to sleep.

426
00:52:07.015 --> 00:52:08.505
I'll keep you company tonight.

427
00:54:13.141 --> 00:54:14.301
Excuse me.

428
00:54:15.610 --> 00:54:17.043
Do you have any toilet paper?

429
00:54:52.047 --> 00:54:53.446
Can I poo first?

430
00:54:53.648 --> 00:54:55.047
I'm sorry.

431
00:56:04.185 --> 00:56:05.413
What's bothering you?

432
00:56:19.267 --> 00:56:20.825
Tun. What's wrong?

433
00:56:32.947 --> 00:56:34.312
What is it?

434
00:57:25.967 --> 00:57:27.229
Is it around here?

435
00:57:38.146 --> 00:57:39.443
Excuse me.

436
00:57:40.048 --> 00:57:41.310
Do you know where this is?

437
00:57:45.720 --> 00:57:47.620
Mom. where is this house?

438
00:58:21.589 --> 00:58:22.851
Ma'am.

439
00:58:35.370 --> 00:58:36.462
Excuse me...

440
00:58:36.704 --> 00:58:38.103
Is this Natre's house?

441
00:58:40.074 --> 00:58:41.234
What do you want?

442
00:58:42.544 --> 00:58:43.568
Well...

443
00:58:43.945 --> 00:58:46.106
We're her friends.

444
00:58:47.081 --> 00:58:49.072
Natre's friends? Come inside.

445
00:59:00.161 --> 00:59:02.629
Have some water. You must be tired.

446
00:59:02.964 --> 00:59:04.556
Did you drive from Bangkok?

447
00:59:05.767 --> 00:59:06.791
Yes.

448
00:59:09.904 --> 00:59:13.931
We'd like to ask about Natre.

449
00:59:14.976 --> 00:59:16.637
She's not feeling well.

450
00:59:17.045 --> 00:59:18.342
She's taking a nap.

451
00:59:19.848 --> 00:59:21.247
Should I wake her?

452
00:59:25.620 --> 00:59:27.212
Stay for dinner.

453
00:59:28.089 --> 00:59:29.317
I was about to cook.

454
00:59:29.524 --> 00:59:31.890
I'm making her favourite dish.

455
00:59:33.595 --> 00:59:35.153
Natre will be so happy.

456
00:59:35.663 --> 00:59:37.494
Her friends don't visit often.

457
00:59:38.099 --> 00:59:39.498
Wait right here.

458
00:59:58.453 --> 00:59:59.715
Where are you going?

459
01:01:14.362 --> 01:01:15.659
How dare you?

460
01:01:21.703 --> 01:01:23.671
Did she commit suicide?

461
01:01:28.609 --> 01:01:30.736
We should cremate her.

462
01:01:32.680 --> 01:01:33.647
No.

463
01:01:33.848 --> 01:01:35.213
I won't cremate her.

464
01:01:37.652 --> 01:01:38.641
Ma'am...

465
01:01:40.288 --> 01:01:43.155
I don't know if you believe such things...

466
01:01:43.624 --> 01:01:46.991
but I'd like you to look at these photos.

467
01:01:47.795 --> 01:01:51.128
They were taken around campus.

468
01:01:53.434 --> 01:01:55.766
Some of the places...

469
01:01:56.537 --> 01:01:59.438
were rooms Natre had been in.

470
01:02:00.274 --> 01:02:04.210
And these shadows appeared

471
01:02:07.782 --> 01:02:09.010
I think that...

472
01:02:10.251 --> 01:02:13.345
Natre's spirit is restless.

473
01:02:14.822 --> 01:02:16.050
Natre...

474
01:02:19.694 --> 01:02:21.161
My dear Natre.

475
01:02:23.364 --> 01:02:25.264
Why don't you visit me?

476
01:02:33.741 --> 01:02:36.141
Can you tell me what happened?

477
01:02:37.045 --> 01:02:38.706
Why she left Bangkok?

478
01:02:47.221 --> 01:02:48.483
Ma'am...

479
01:02:50.725 --> 01:02:51.885
Ma'am.

480
01:02:53.261 --> 01:02:54.888
These shadows...

481
01:02:55.463 --> 01:02:58.796
might mean her spirit is not at peace.

482
01:03:03.137 --> 01:03:05.332
We should hold her funeral.

483
01:03:06.874 --> 01:03:08.205
Please.

484
01:03:22.390 --> 01:03:23.618
When she came home...

485
01:03:23.825 --> 01:03:25.258
she seemed different.

486
01:03:25.626 --> 01:03:27.389
She wouldn't talk to anyone.

487
01:03:27.962 --> 01:03:29.953
No one knows what happened in Bangkok.

488
01:03:31.933 --> 01:03:34.094
Then she overdosed on pills.

489
01:03:34.802 --> 01:03:37.202
Luckily. her mother found her...

490
01:03:37.572 --> 01:03:39.437
and got her to the hospital on time.

491
01:03:39.941 --> 01:03:42.205
When she recovered...

492
01:03:43.544 --> 01:03:46.411
she climbed on the hospital roof...

493
01:03:47.048 --> 01:03:48.572
and jumped off the edge.

494
01:03:50.751 --> 01:03:53.515
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

495
01:03:55.623 --> 01:03:58.854
She's been distraught
ever since Natre's death.

496
01:03:59.594 --> 01:04:03.257
No matter what she refused to cremate her.

497
01:04:04.599 --> 01:04:06.794
All the villagers were scared.

498
01:04:07.168 --> 01:04:09.966
No one wanted to socialize with her.

499
01:06:12.693 --> 01:06:13.921
Can't sleep?

500
01:06:19.734 --> 01:06:21.793
Tell me the truth...

501
01:06:22.770 --> 01:06:24.431
Did you love Natre?

502
01:06:28.242 --> 01:06:29.971
I tried to...

503
01:06:36.250 --> 01:06:38.741
I believed that one day I would.

504
01:06:44.492 --> 01:06:46.392
But I was fooling myself.

505
01:06:54.402 --> 01:06:55.835
When I broke it off...

506
01:06:57.071 --> 01:06:59.505
I was a total asshole.

507
01:07:05.513 --> 01:07:07.447
But she still loved me the same.

508
01:07:14.021 --> 01:07:15.852
I want this to be over.

509
01:07:17.925 --> 01:07:20.359
If she wants me to die I will.

510
01:07:21.429 --> 01:07:23.090
Don't say that.

511
01:07:24.098 --> 01:07:25.690
It's almost over.

512
01:07:27.068 --> 01:07:28.194
No it's not.

513
01:07:33.374 --> 01:07:35.638
I know she'll come for me.

514
01:07:36.544 --> 01:07:37.602
Tun.

515
01:07:38.512 --> 01:07:40.173
We've come this far.

516
01:07:42.516 --> 01:07:44.484
And you're sorry for what you did.

517
01:07:45.453 --> 01:07:47.011
I'm sure she knows.

518
01:07:49.390 --> 01:07:51.017
Don't talk about death anymore.

519
01:07:58.132 --> 01:07:59.531
I'm sorry.

520
01:08:05.172 --> 01:08:06.935
Do you still love me?

521
01:08:12.880 --> 01:08:15.713
No matter what you won't leave me. right?

522
01:09:54.915 --> 01:09:56.940
Jane.

523
01:11:30.044 --> 01:11:31.341
Tun...

524
01:11:31.712 --> 01:11:32.701
Jane...

525
01:11:33.247 --> 01:11:34.737
Where did you go?

526
01:11:36.050 --> 01:11:37.540
Why did you leave me alone?

527
01:11:38.452 --> 01:11:39.544
We've got to leave.

528
01:11:43.157 --> 01:11:44.556
Asshole!

529
01:11:45.793 --> 01:11:47.260
Why did you leave me?

530
01:11:47.461 --> 01:11:49.156
Didn't you love me?

531
01:11:49.597 --> 01:11:50.894
How could you leave me?

532
01:11:53.968 --> 01:11:55.833
How could you leave me?

533
01:13:35.169 --> 01:13:36.363
Tun...

534
01:13:36.737 --> 01:13:38.295
Are you feeling better?

535
01:13:40.841 --> 01:13:42.832
What happened last night?

536
01:13:44.311 --> 01:13:45.369
Tun...

537
01:13:47.047 --> 01:13:48.014
Jane...

538
01:13:48.215 --> 01:13:49.341
Jane...

539
01:13:56.490 --> 01:13:57.422
The abbot said...

540
01:13:57.624 --> 01:13:59.592
Natre will be cremated today.

541
01:14:03.230 --> 01:14:04.788
It's over.

542
01:16:00.681 --> 01:16:02.239
- Hello.
- Hello. Jane.

543
01:16:02.850 --> 01:16:03.874
Picking up photos?

544
01:16:04.685 --> 01:16:05.583
Where's Tun?

545
01:16:05.786 --> 01:16:07.014
He's busy.

546
01:16:07.487 --> 01:16:08.579
Good.

547
01:16:08.789 --> 01:16:09.619
When he's busy...

548
01:16:09.823 --> 01:16:11.290
I get to see you.

549
01:16:19.399 --> 01:16:20.730
You went on vacation?

550
01:16:21.568 --> 01:16:22.626
To the beach.

551
01:16:23.170 --> 01:16:24.296
When did you go?

552
01:16:25.005 --> 01:16:26.529
Last week.

553
01:16:28.876 --> 01:16:30.867
This photo is...

554
01:16:34.381 --> 01:16:35.541
What's wrong?

555
01:16:41.722 --> 01:16:42.950
You look fatter.

556
01:16:45.325 --> 01:16:46.724
I didn't recognize you.

557
01:16:49.229 --> 01:16:50.196
Hi.

558
01:16:51.198 --> 01:16:52.392
Jumbo prints.

559
01:16:54.101 --> 01:16:55.329
Write you name. please.

560
01:19:34.795 --> 01:19:36.057
Get her guys!

561
01:20:11.731 --> 01:20:12.823
Jane...

562
01:20:13.233 --> 01:20:14.962
Why are you crying?

563
01:20:17.871 --> 01:20:18.963
Asshole...

564
01:20:21.575 --> 01:20:23.543
How could you be so cruel?

565
01:20:29.182 --> 01:20:30.615
Where did you find these?

566
01:20:33.220 --> 01:20:34.812
If I didn't find them...

567
01:20:35.021 --> 01:20:37.251
I'd be a fool forever. right?

568
01:20:42.863 --> 01:20:44.353
Let me explain.

569
01:20:47.601 --> 01:20:49.296
What's there to say?

570
01:20:53.640 --> 01:20:55.232
I always believed you.

571
01:21:02.349 --> 01:21:04.283
I thought I knew you.

572
01:21:18.265 --> 01:21:19.323
Tun.

573
01:21:20.567 --> 01:21:21.693
Take her picture...

574
01:21:21.968 --> 01:21:23.162
so she doesn't blab.

575
01:21:23.370 --> 01:21:25.361
Tun. help me.

576
01:21:27.040 --> 01:21:28.200
I know it was wrong.

577
01:21:29.843 --> 01:21:31.640
Take her picture now!

578
01:21:32.812 --> 01:21:33.938
What's wrong!

579
01:21:35.482 --> 01:21:36.949
I'm your buddy!

580
01:21:37.450 --> 01:21:38.474
Hurry!

581
01:21:47.160 --> 01:21:48.991
Tun. help me.

582
01:22:02.442 --> 01:22:03.739
I never forgave myself.

583
01:22:03.944 --> 01:22:05.912
But I was young and stupid.

584
01:22:07.480 --> 01:22:08.845
I've heard enough.

585
01:22:10.951 --> 01:22:12.441
I'm going home.

586
01:23:07.340 --> 01:23:08.671
Come on out!

587
01:23:13.480 --> 01:23:14.845
Where are you?

588
01:23:21.388 --> 01:23:23.015
I thought you loved me!

589
01:23:25.358 --> 01:23:27.053
Loved me so much!

590
01:23:34.534 --> 01:23:36.729
